c: 16
v: 80
t: "Uye Allah vakakugadzirirai mudzimba dzenyu pekugara, uye vakakugadzirirai kubva kumatehwe emombe dzimba (matende), dzamunoona dzakareruka pamunofamba uye nepamunogara (munguva dzekufamba); uye kubva kumakushe adzo, mambava nemvere (hwai, ngamera nembudzi) midziyo nemufaro kwenguva diki"